                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-11-defend185 t18290115-11-punish54"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 18.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Prosecutor, believing it to be his first offence.</p>
